oy it anymore.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While Djokovic is not going anywhere just yet, the same can not be said for Andy Murray and Rafael Nadal.Murray has confirmed he will be quitting tennis after the Olympics, while Nadal is widely expected to retire later in the year.LATEST SPORTS NEWS:Charlotte Dujardin horse whipping video was 'timed to cause maximum damage' ahead of Paris OlympicsEngland could be about to shoot themselves in the foot with next manager search after Gareth Southgate exitAnthony Joshua has been 'exposed' after 'getting a bit too nasty' as Carl Froch reveals latest on boxing feudNovak Djokovic has sent messages to Andy Murray and Rafael Nadal as he prepares to play at the Olympics this summer|PADjokovic has lost two Grand Slam finals to Murray over the years - but has wished his rival well for the future as he prepares to embark on a new challenge.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 3118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2284, \"end\": 2292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999410736127, \"rank\": 5.8926392672086445e-08, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8533452503197173e-56, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2457, \"end\": 2462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999927815679, \"rank\": 7.2185418160910935e-09, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nad