resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 2880, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8533452503197173e-56, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2896, \"end\": 2908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2990, \"end\": 2994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poetry_slam\", \"score\": 0.797472821313158, \"rank\": 0.2539612301186532, \"text\": \"Slam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poetry_slam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poetry_slam\"}, {\"begin\": 3005, \"end\": 3011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3514672712110223e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I heard the news about Andy and I hope that he will have the best possible farewell in his last competitive match here in Olympics for him and his country,\\\" he stated.\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He is a legend of our sport, he's been an incredibly important player for tennis globally.\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And Djokovic hopes Nadal can keep playing, with the pair on course to meet in the second round of the games in France.Novak Djokovic is hoping to win Olympic gold for the first time this summer|PA\\\"Nadal of course the same, even more, all the results and achievements he has had, particularly in this city in Roland Garros,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3382, \"end\": 3390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999410736127, \"rank\": 5.8926392672086445e-08, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 3397, \"end\": 3402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999927815679, \"rank\": 7.2185418160910935e-09, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 3502, \"end\": 3510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999410736127, \"rank\": 5.8926392672086445e-08, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 3686, \"end\": 3699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.765428553527353e-14, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nadal still did not say when his last tournament will be so hopefully, for the sake of the sport, he can keep going.\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Djokovic is yet to win Olympic gold so far, despite everything else he's achieved.And whether he's able to finally claim that elusive honour remains to be seen.\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was beaten by Jannik Sinner at the Australian Open back in January, with the 22-year-old proceeding to lift the trophy.\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 4112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4007, \"end\": 4020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jannik Sinner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic was then forced to pull out of the French Open due to injury and, though he fared well at Wimbledon, he wascrushed by Carlos Alcaraz in the final of that prestigious competitionearlier this month.\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4241, \"end\": 4255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Novak Djokovic has opened up ahead of the Paris Olympics  PA  Given his age, some feel the 24-time Grand Slam winner is approaching the end of his glittering career.\", \"from\": 4321, \"to\": 4486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4321, \"end\": 4335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet Djokovic, speaking ahead of the Olympics, has now made it clear he has no plans to walk away from the sport just yet.\", \"from\": 4488, \"to\": 4609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\":